name: White Strap Sandles
description: These are white wedge heel, open toe Sandles,Very nice for the summer or those relaxing holiday breaks! would go nice with jeans, skirts or shorts of any kind! Brand new from new look, never worn and the labels are still on x

name: New Look Satin Top
description: This is a gorgeous satin open detailed top with an elastic band around the waist to give definition to the waist line. it has strings at the back of the neck line to do up and the material flows over the shoulders. this could be worn with a top underneath or if brave enough on its own!!!! This kind of detailed top never gets old in the fashion industry and can look amazing on anyone!

name: New Look Shirt Dress
description: This is a shirt dress that can be worn on its own to complement those lovely legs of yours or over a pair of jeans or linin trousers! Also perfect for the crazy nights out dressing up as army girls as it is a raw green with also a belt that has sparkles on it. It has quather length arms with pockets along the bottom of the garment and also at the top.

name: Checked Shirt/Dress
description: This is a shirt dress that can be worn on its own or over a pair of jeans or linin trousers!Nice in the summer as it has nice suttle colours within the garment. It has quather length arms with a tie around material belt to match the item.
